general.gigTitle: be your full stack web developer or do website development javascript

sellerCard.description:
Hi there! 
I'm a full-stack website developer with extensive experience working in various freelancing marketplaces.
My main goal is always to provide the highest quality services to my clients.

I specialize in front-end technologies such as Nextjs, ReactJS, Redux, React Native, Context API, HTML/CSS, and Vanilla JS, as well as back-end technologies like NodeJS, ExpressJS, Handlebars, EJS, Pug, and REST APIs. 
I also have experience working with databases like MongoDB and MySQL, and am proficient in using tools like Git, Github, Bitbucket, Putty, Highcharts, D3Js, AWS, Docker, and Kubernetes.

description.content:
Hi,

I am Muhammad a senior Javascript developer.


Looking for a sleek, innovative, and responsive website? You've found the right expert. With over 4 years in web development, I've assisted more than 150 clients worldwide.


Services I Offer: 

  • Design using HTML CSS Tailwind or Bootstrap.
  • Third-party API Integration 
  • Website Design Customization
  • E-Commerce site Designing and Development
  • Listing site Development 
  • LMS Designing and Development 
  • Social Media sites
  • Marketplace websites such as Fiverr/Upwork/Airbnb
  • Feature of Membership.
  • Functionality Modification
  • Content uploading 
  • News Website 
  • Admin Panels to manage orders, users, products, and banner
  • Real-time time analytics
  • Host to Aws, Hostinger, C panel, Digital Ocean, Railway, Vercel, etc.
  • Responsive to all Devices Phones and Tablets 


Languages and frameworks I use:

  • Html Css
  • Javascript
  • Nodejs
  • Reactjs/Nextjs
  • Mongodb/MySql


These are the latest and best technologies to use in your project.

Big companies like Netflix, Twitch, and Nike use Next.js to develop their sites.


Note: The Final cost will vary depending on the unique features and functionalities you require for your website. For a detailed quote, feel free to reach out
